query:
SELECT e.id, e.turmaId, e.tipoEvento, e.dataEvento, e.dataEventoFim, e.local, l.nome as localNome
FROM eventos e
LEFT JOIN locais l ON e.local = l.id
WHERE e.turmaId = 654
ORDER BY e.dataEvento;
